7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Blackbox AI and Mutable AI share a solid foundation of core features including Code Generation, Multi Language, Chat. Where Blackbox AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Autocomplete and Ide Integration, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Mutable AI uniquely offers Refactoring and Documentation, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Blackbox AI holds an overall score of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Mutable AI scores 6/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Blackbox AI offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $0, compared to Mutable AI's starting price of $12/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Blackbox AI's free tier and Mutable AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
